            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName key="#Salian"><name ref="Perisinda/Beza">Perisinda que
                                Bettia vocatur</name></persName> filia bone memorie <persName
                            key="#Salian"><name ref="Tursinglo">Tursinglo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Salian">ex genere Francorum</rs> (…) secundum <rs key="#Salian"
                            >legiem mea saligam</rs> actramentario pinna et pergamena cum
                        actramentario manibus meis de terra levavi et <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary #Judge"><name ref="Rodulfus"
                            >Rodulfi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> et <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> donni
                        imperatoris ad scribendam tradedit et scribere rogavit per wasone terre
                        fistucum nodatum seo ramum arboribus adque per cultellum et wantonem seo
                        andelaine, offre pro dei amore et remedium anime mee et pro anima bone
                        memorie <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/207">Rodulfi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">com(itis)</rs> et <persName key="#Countess"
                            ref="#people/208">Ermingarde</persName> qui fuit <rs key="#Countess"
                            >comitissa</rs> iugalibus, et pro anima <persName key="#Countess"
                            ref="#people/209">Matilde</persName> et <persName ref="#people/182"
                            >Imilde</persName> germane filie suprascripti Rodulfi (…) beati <orgName
                            key="#Churches #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/79">Sancti Petro
                            principis apostolorum</orgName> sito loco <placeName
                            key="#Churches #Monasteries" ref="#places/285">Palatiolo</placeName>
                        prope <placeName key="#Churches #Monasteries" ref="#places/85">Monte
                            Virde</placeName>, ut deus et dominus noster Iesu Christo ut peccatis de
                        suprascripti iugalibus aliquis minuare presummat (…) quattuor inter <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casis et cascinis et rebus meis illis
                            massariciis</rs> quam abeo in loco et finibus nucupantur duo ex ipsis
                        casis et rebus sunt positis in loco <placeName
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">Sussiano</placeName>, una regitur per
                        filii bone memorie <persName><name ref="Falipertus"
                        >Flaipi</name></persName>; et illa secunda detinetur per filio bone memorie
                                <persName><name ref="Teulus">Teuli</name></persName>; et illa tertia
                        cascina et res in <placeName key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            ref="#places/286">Veclinne</placeName> qui regiere videtur per
                                <persName><name ref="Venerus">Veneri</name></persName> massario; et
                        illa quarta casa et res ubi dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">Muscleta</placeName>, quod regere
                        videtur per <persName><name ref="Martinus">Martino</name></persName>, con
                        tutte le loro dipendenze; offre poi meam portionem ex integram de <rs
                            key="#Casalini/fundamenta">fundamento et casalino</rs> qui fuit
                                <persName><name ref="Liutbertus">Liuberti</name></persName> quam
                        abeo in loco et finibus ubi dicitur <placeName key="#Casalini/fundamenta"
                            ref="#places/286">Veclinne</placeName> (la quota è la metà), con tutte
                        le sue dipendenze; offre inoltre a suprascripta <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesia</rs> et <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs> Sancti Petri
                        idest una <rs key="#Petiae">petia</rs> de terra, quod est <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vinea</rs> mea illa, quam abeo in suprascripto loco <placeName
                            key="#Petiae #Wine" ref="#places/286">Veclinne</placeName>, qui uno capo
                        sunt tenentes in terra <persName key="#Confinia #Petiae"><name ref="Rotius"
                                >Roti</name></persName> filio bone memorie <persName><name
                                ref="Ingitius">Inghiti</name></persName>, et alio capo tenet in
                        terra <persName key="#Confinia #Petiae"><name ref="Hugo"
                            >Ughi</name></persName> filio bone memorie <persName><name ref="Winizo"
                                >Winiti</name></persName>, et alio lato tenet in terra de <persName
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae" ref="#people/182">filia</persName> bone memorie
                        suprascripti <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/207">Rodulfi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comitis</rs>, con tutte le sue dipendenze; la donazione è
                        fatta pro anima del donatore et bone memorie Rodulfi comitis et Ermingarde
                        qui fuerunt iugalibus et pro anima bone memorie Matilde qui fuit <rs
                            key="#Countess">comitissa</rs> et Imilde germane; se qualcuno agisse a
                        suo nome per hanc cartulam scripta ex manibus Iohannes notarius domni
                        imperatoris ex comparationem obvenit da suprascripto Rodulfo sicut in ipsa
                        cartula legitur, dovà pagare la pena contenuta nella carta, cioè optimum
                        aurum libras sex, argentum ponderas decem e d’oro e 10 ponderas di argento.
                        Pena per la donazione in duplum. Chiede a Rodulfo notarius et iudex domni
                        imperatoris la stesura della cartula. Actum <placeName ref="#places/285"
                            >loco monasterio Sancti Petri</placeName>. Testimoni: <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Ingelelmus">Inghilelmi</name></persName> filio
                        bone memorie item <persName><name ref="Ingelelmus"
                            >Inghilelmi</name></persName>; <persName key="#Witness #Notary"><name
                                ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarii</rs>; <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Walpertus">Walberti</name></persName> filio bone memorie
                                <persName><name ref="Gunderamus">Gunterami</name></persName>;
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Rainerius">Raineri</name></persName>
                        filio bone memorie <persName><name ref="Ingelelmus"
                            >Inghilelmi</name></persName>; <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Albertus">Alberto</name></persName> filio bone memorie
                                <persName><name ref="Ingelelmus">Inghilelmi</name></persName>.
                        Scrive: Rodulfi notarius et iudex domni imperatoris. </ab>
                        </div>
